title: 6-car crash causing heavy delays on I-93 north - Massachusetts news
text:
Mass. State Police responded to a six-car crash on Interstate 93 north near Hanover Street in Boston at about 1:40 p.m. The crash has resulted in heavy delays. No injuries have been reported.
Rt 93N #Boston @ Hanover St right lane closed for 6 car crash. NO Injuries. Heavy #MAtraffic delays from South Bay.
